tutorialPages.messageText: NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "15A85BA9454804533F8B18BB8E59E16B", "The Warehouse is your private storage for items, resources, and cargo in each node. To access your warehouse, speak to a Warehouse Vendor in a node that is a Village or larger.")

NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "E14EA245415FD7946AFE3C80AA8ABB58", "Items stored in your warehouse are only accessible from the node they are stored in. You can see what you have stored in other Nodes, but you can\'t interact with them.")

NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "7D0C454B471A92898076B0BEDF2DCB45", "Additional storage space can be purchased through the warehouse vendor. The number of storage upgrades available will depend on the node\'s rank and your citizenship status.")
